title._content: Group of men and women working from a Pauls Ice Cream and Milk stall in Brisbane

description._content: Creator: Unidentified Location:Brisbane, Queensland Description: A woman and two men can be seen standing behind the decorated servery of a Pauls Ice Cream and Milk stall in a Brisbane park. Signage for Pauls Ice Cream & Milk Ltd is clearly displayed above and below the servery bench of the stall. Another two women wearing day dresses and aprons can be seen chatting to the stall attendants behind the serving counter where drink bottles have been placed.
